The paper deals with the problem of selecting representative instances from large and massively-distributed data, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. The paper proposes a fast and accurate greedy algorithm for column subset selection, which is a fundamental problem in these fields. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DM (Data Mining), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
